{
  "stem": "3085.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Beyond that, he would measure everything on-- I mean, they had the-- he, he, he was-- he was really-- I understand he was an anthropologist by, by, by--",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Training.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--training, if you like.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he did all sorts of measurements on anything from, you know, the head and the eyes.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, and I know one of the most unpleasant things that I can recall was when he took impressions of our teeth.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because I recall that we had to-- they probably used plaster of Paris or some gypsum, some kind of material like calcium sulfate.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, and of course, they filled our teeth, our, our mouth.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was extremely unpleasant.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I mean, I had to have my mouth-- I was gagging and-- for several hours until that thing dried.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they took it out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That was-- that, that imprint, that stayed with me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And, and I'm, I'm still kind of-- I still have a phobia about gagging, probably from that time on.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But that was one of the more unpleasant things that they did.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "As I say, they measured everything and-- from head to toe.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And, and he didn't necessarily do everything himself.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I mean, he had assistants.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Sometimes he did it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Sometimes he would just watch it, and the assistants would do it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So it wasn't necessarily him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But he, he always supervised it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I mean, he was obviously in charge.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He may have.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, I don't speak-- I didn't speak German.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I, I spoke a little German.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I suppose I understood-- no, not much.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I understand he-- as I recall, he spoke a few words Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, you know, he, he, he could be-- he was a very, very interesting character.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
